quite interesting gameplay.

00:00:24.189 --> 00:00:30.009
Very very Japanese style as you might
expect

00:00:30.009 --> 00:00:34.410
from having a slightly crazy name that I think
gets lost in translation somewhere.

00:00:34.410 --> 00:00:39.280
The idea is giant robots. Giant robots with guns, enemy robots with guns,

00:00:39.280 --> 00:00:40.660
