00:00:56.860 --> 00:01:01.520
The graphics are really fast paced, 
quite fun

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:08.520
gameplay as well but quite challenging,
it's a difficult, difficult  game.

00:01:11.530 --> 00:01:14.740
You get power-ups as you go along, and
there are giant bosses

00:01:14.740 --> 00:01:18.450
at the end which are going to require quite a 
bit of concentration and 

00:01:18.450 --> 00:01:20.410
skill to actually beat.

00:01:20.410 --> 00:01:24.780
Like any Bullet Storm Hell game, it's
quite tricky made even more difficult
I suppose

00:01:24.780 --> 00:01:28.430
because it's in 3D so you're kind of having 
to think about

00:01:28.430 --> 00:01:30.590
a whole lot more while you play

00:01:30.590 --> 00:01:34.009
and talking becomes difficult.

